#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:1
msgid "E4210"
msgstr "E4210"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `regex_alias_in_alternation`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`regex_alias_in_alternation`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:5
msgid "Regex alias is not allowed inside an alternation branch."
msgstr "正则别名不能出现在交替分支内部。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:7
msgid ""
"In a regex match expression, `as` binds the matched text. When the "
"pattern uses alternation with `|`, bind the whole alternation instead of "
"binding only one branch. Otherwise the binder would exist only for some "
"alternatives."
msgstr ""
"在正则匹配表达式中，`as` 会绑定匹配到的文本。当模式使用 `|` 进行交替匹配时，"
"应绑定整个交替模式，而不是只绑定其中一个分支。否则该绑定只会在部分分支中存"
"在。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:13
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ ((re\"a\" as left) | re\"b\"))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:17
msgid "`left` is bound only when the first branch matches."
msgstr "只有第一个分支匹配时，`left` 才会被绑定。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:19
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:21
msgid ""
"Move the alias outside the alternation so it is defined no matter which "
"branch matches."
msgstr "将别名移到交替模式外部，使其无论哪个分支匹配都会被定义。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4210.md:24
msgid ""
"fn match_text(s : String) -> Unit {\n"
"  ignore(s =~ ((re\"a\" | re\"b\") as either))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
